WEBVTT

00:00:08.001 --> 00:00:09.281
Little do they know it,

00:00:09.281 --> 00:00:15.721
but these six creatures are each about to
experience a very unusual death.

00:00:15.721 --> 00:00:16.621
One-by-one,

00:00:16.621 --> 00:00:20.451
they will fall prey to the remarkable, 
predatory antics of...

00:00:20.451 --> 00:00:22.921
a carnivorous plant.

00:00:22.921 --> 00:00:26.391
Around the world there are more than 
600 plant species

00:00:26.391 --> 00:00:30.571
that supplement a regular 
diet of sunlight, water, and soil